Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.messages

Record Class StartGameMessage.StartGamePayload

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
it.polimi.ingsw.model.messages.StartGameMessage.StartGamePayload
Record Components:
board - The board
players - The list of players playing
currentPlayer - The nickname of the current player
personalGoalId - The id of the personal goal of the client receiving the message
CGXIndex - The index of the common goal X
topCGXScore - The score on the top of the stack of the common goal X
CGYIndex - The index of the common goal Y
topCGYScore - The score on the top of the stack of the common goal Y
All Implemented Interfaces:
